{
  "name": "morie",
  "version": "0.9.7",
  "summary": "Multi-domain scientific computing toolkit (Python + R) for observational inference and intervention analysis, hosting the MRM (Multilevel Reconciliation Methodology) framework for Canadian carceral, police, and oversight data. Provides causal estimators (ATE, ATT, AIPW, DML, G-computation), survey sampling, propensity-score and doubly-robust methods, sensitivity analysis, spatial statistics, Hawkes point processes, and psychometrics, with a unified RichResult output.",
